  "description": "The hero preset. The moment light breaks through clouds. Zero attack for instant impact, bright filter, no shimmer at defaults — but the GLOW macro fades shimmer in from zero to full. At rest it is a bold, present supersaw. Turn GLOW and it blooms into infinite radiance. The Guru says: the best presets are journeys, not destinations. This one starts on the ground and ends in the sky.",
